{"tid":476622,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN]蒼天英雄誌 新ser ios上市 !","createTime":"2017-11-22T07:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T08:52:02.000Z","uid":48615,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8756008c70010f2cade506177751c91fabb432f","tid":476622,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WT8s5E8w9Nw/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FWT8s5E8w9Nw%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=4cd22ca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【遊戲背景】<br />\n蒼天已死，亂世將至，堪比三國時代的連年征戰討伐，民不聊生，蠱惑人心的邪教趁機而起紛紛在各地作亂，造成天下一片混沌。<br />\n某日大地發生巨變，沉潛千年的魔主被邪術召喚而甦醒，劃破天際橫空出世，魔主自喻梟雄曹操，決意殺戮眾生吞噬天下稱霸為王！此時，遙遠的國度有位英雄挺身而出，為了拯救天下蒼生，展開熱血刺激的冒險篇章，自此踏上殲滅魔主的不歸旅程，並決心成為蒼天英雄！<br />\n<br />\n【遊戲特色】<br />\n◆あの人気武将が美麗カードになって登場！<br />\n近百位知名經典武將，各有不同屬性及技能等你收集！創新玩法幻形系統，透過幻形功能轉變武將性別，知名武將綺麗化變身女性，除此之外遊戲內的語音及外觀視覺將大幅改變，給玩家前所未有的遊戲體驗。<br />\n<br />\n◆豪華日本声優陣ボイス！<br />\n遊戲由日本頂級聲優助陣--釘宮理惠、內田真禮、松岡禎丞、下野紘等全程日語錄製配音，聲優們運用各自聲線特色和精湛專業的聲音表情，詮釋每位武將的究極奧義，玩家更能身歷其境享受遊戲磅礡故事劇情及副本內容！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/ACG/c/75/0000091875.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2FACG%2Fc%2F75%2F0000091875.PNG&h=280fe07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隻game唔算有首抽 唔係唔可以刷不過前面都幾長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下面會貼建議開始既將<br />\n可以抽3－5個十連先 <br />\n新入game巴打可以入去活動拉到最底打我既推薦碼會有250點<br />\n同加我好友: 尋獲最後審判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推薦碼：bqc92<br />\n人多可以開公會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n我係s8－決戰虎牢"},{"pid":"db91f934e528498e8265ea9b832f84ed496ff34f","tid":476622,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bde462b1f7d22a01a8158b99d5a7e3ce1c3dd83","tid":476622,"uid":91195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:30:32.000Z","msg":"隻game玩乜"},{"pid":"ae6f679a7870cfc6f7ed85af9147ba4846588c27","tid":476622,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻game玩乜</blockquote><br />\n用5隻三國武將砌陣<br />\n打關卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea13e171333ee2fefbbbe3e2f46abd3e922ed7e4","tid":476622,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28f80ee603dc4235081da3affa0d3a1a8c8b8ec","tid":476622,"uid":48615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}